      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable dings, some paint fading on the hood, and minor scuffs on the bumpers, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery and some cracked plastic trim. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but the transmission shifts a bit firmly and the tires will likely need replacement within the next year. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a few cosmetic flaws and minor deferred maintenance.",
