      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, this vehicle is offered in pristine, showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and showing no discernible signs of wear, it represents the pinnacle of its class. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, adheres to the most rigorous standards of preservation. This is an uncompromising choice for the collector or enthusiast who demands absolute perfection. We invite serious inquiries to inspect this investment-grade motorcar.",
      "price": 48500.0,
