    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or imperfections, while the interior remains in showroom state, even retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every surface, from the supple, uncreased leather seating to the high-definition infotainment display, is in pristine condition. Mechanically, the car is flawless, accompanied by a comprehensive folder of service records from certified technicians. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule vehicle that delivers a factory-fresh driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
