    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total gem. This car has been my baby\u2014always kept in the garage and pampered since day one. It looks and drives like it\u2019s brand new, with a flawless interior and that perfect showroom shine. I\u2019m looking for a quick, smooth sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to move! Come check it out and see for yourself how gorgeous it is\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
