    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an impeccably preserved E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. The S54B32 inline-six remains in peak tune, exhibiting perfect compression and smooth VANOS actuation across the rev range. This example features a reinforced rear subframe and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission linked to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is stock and tight, with all bushings and dampers providing the communicative feedback expected of a low-mileage chassis. The original paintwork is free of swirl marks, and the interior is devoid of typical bolster wear or trim delamination. Mechanical provenance is documented, including critical preventative rod bearing maintenance.",
